    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"> <p>Here at more onion we're hosting most of our client's sites ourselves. This means we are hosting lots of sites which share most of their modules (ie. our standard Drupal installation). Reproducible setups, fast builds, sharing-module code among many sites -- This is where our new <a href="https://github.com/torotil/dbuild.py">build-tool called dbuild.py</a> comes in.</p>
